# Backend Rules

## API
- Use REST + WebSocket
- Use typed responses
- Use Zod validation

## Security
- Never expose secrets
- Validate all inputs
- Use rate limiting

## Database
- Use Prisma ORM
- Use migrations properly
- Avoid N+1 queries

## Redis
- Cache expensive API calls
- Store websocket snapshots

## Error Handling
- Standard error response format
- Add retry logic
- Add logging

## Performance
- Use parallel API fetching
- Avoid blocking operations